rows.label: qev086504_MSG0001
rows.name: Mamapon![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev086504_MSG0002
rows.name: Tatsu![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev086504_MSG0003
rows.name: Thank you! Friends save life of Koko![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev086504_MSG0004
rows.name: Mamapon, what happened to big fish for littlepon?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev086504_MSG0005
rows.name:
Ah, yes... Well, it became snack for
ugly critter friends just pounded.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev086504_MSG0006
rows.name: Awww...what will littlepon eat?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev086504_MSG0007
rows.name:
Why, ugly critter of course! Now be good
Tatsu and help Mamapon carry it home.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev086504_JNK0010
rows.name: Nod

rows.label: qev086504_SEL0011
rows.name: Note that mothers are nothing to mess with.

rows.label: qev086504_JNK0020
rows.name: Drool

rows.label: qev086504_SEL0021
rows.name: Admire how tasty the indigen looks.

rows.label: qev086504_MSG0008
rows.name: No kidding. We probably didn't even need to help.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev086504_MSG0009
rows.name: That's... Wow, yeah. I've never cooked one of those before.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev086504_MSG0010
rows.name: But either way, you're trying it before me.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev086504_MSG0011
rows.name:
Tatsu? Didn't Commander Vandham
have something for you to ask?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev086504_MSG0012
rows.name: Meh! Tatsu almost completely forget![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev086504_MSG0012_2
rows.name: Mamapon...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev086504_MSG0013
rows.name:
Mustache man and rest of New LA have
request for Dodonga Caravan.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev086504_MSG0014
rows.name: They want Mamapon to sign treaty brought by emissary.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev086504_MSG0015
rows.name: Meaty bought by cemetery?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev086504_MSG0016
rows.name:
He's referring to an agreement that our city
and your caravan would become allies, Koko.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev086504_MSG0017
rows.name: Oh-ho? Well then. Sound lovely.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev086504_MSG0018
rows.name: Then Mamapon need to sign treaty![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev086504_MSG0019
rows.name: Okay. Koko has signed.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev086504_MSG0020
rows.name: Now big city and Dodonga Caravan best of friends.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev086504_MSG0021
rows.name: Yay![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev086504_MSG0022
rows.name: We appreciate your cooperation.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev086504_MSG0023
rows.name: Next up, Dorian Caravan. Time to get treaty finished.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev086504_MSG0024
rows.name:
That complete crucial and important mission!
Now we report back to mustache man.[ST:wait ]
